# 🪄 Magic Recon - Automation Framework
> **Comprehensive shell-based framework for automated reconnaissance and data aggregation.**

### 📥 Deployment Process
```bash
# Clone the repository and initialize the installation script
git clone [https://github.com/joseph-reid/magic-recon.git](https://github.com/joseph-reid/magic-recon.git)
cd magic-recon
chmod +x install.sh
sudo ./install.sh

Bash
# Initiate an automated recon workflow for a specific domain
./magicrecon.sh -d target.com
